# Apple Developer secrets (APNs auth keys, signing certs, CSRs).
# The .p8 file is downloadable only ONCE from Apple Developer Console
# at key creation time — losing it means revoking + re-creating, so
# treat it like a secret. Same for .cer / .certSigningRequest.
Apple keys/
*.p8
*.cer
*.certSigningRequest

